To install this SDK, see [Add Firebase to your project.](https://firebase.google.com/docs/ios/setup)

## Note
8.12.0 does not exist for the Firebase CocoaPod or Swift Package Manager. An issue was discovered during the rollout (with an unpublished pod) so we skipped the rest and moved to 8.12.1 instead of moving the CocoaPods-8.12.0 tag. Apologies if this causes any confusion.
